description: Retrieves information about a specific email address that's on the suppression list for your account.

parameters.name: EmailAddress
parameters.description: The email address that's on the account suppression list.

nested_items.name: SuppressedDestination
nested_items.description: An object containing information about the suppressed email address.

nested_items.name: EmailAddress
nested_items.description: The email address that is on the suppression list for your account.

nested_items.name: Reason
nested_items.description: The reason that the address was added to the suppression list for your account.

nested_items.name: LastUpdateTime
nested_items.description: The date and time when the suppressed destination was last updated, shown in Unix time format.

nested_items.name: Attributes
nested_items.description: An optional value that can contain additional information about the reasons that the address was added to the suppression list for your account.

nested_items.name: MessageId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the email message that caused the email address to be added to the suppression list for your account.

nested_items.name: FeedbackId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier that's generated when an email address is added to the suppression list for your account.
